  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a lot of stuff to add to Ooglians, and we want <strong>YOU</strong> to be a part of the process! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Community feedback is key for prioritizing what to work on next, such as</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand base building</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add more ooglian types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polish existing gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add non-gameplay stuff like stats, achievements, high-score</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Head on over to our Discord and let us know what you want to see in the game next!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/8b57c326bec49fe277d66fb78be9c232.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/8b57c326bec49fe277d66fb78be9c232.webm?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/8b57c326bec49fe277d66fb78be9c232.mp4?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The tower defense base builder you never realized you wanted!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Straight out of a fever dream, here is... Ooglians!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What are Ooglians?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/81dc9084c9392762f394fd37e2dda0fd.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/81dc9084c9392762f394fd37e2dda0fd.webm?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/81dc9084c9392762f394fd37e2dda0fd.mp4?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Ooglians are a mysterious species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's unknown whether they are technophobes or destructophiles,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >but they sure love smashing machinery to bits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are not an Ooglian.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/6b8c51e499e549720826584b0ad0bca8.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/6b8c51e499e549720826584b0ad0bca8.webm?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>You are... you. It's not up to me to tell you who you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Why</i> are you on this planet?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What</i> is your goal?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is, as of now, unknown. Maybe if you protect your reactor, you'll find out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Build the base around your reactor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Ooglians are attracted by the machinery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Ooglians try to destroy your base</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/06366c8727c328e12443157e635dc980.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/06366c8727c328e12443157e635dc980.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Build more machines to defend your base</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Attract more ooglians</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> It's a game loop</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.apng?t=1773046905\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> You lose <span class=\"bb_strike\">when</span> if your reactor dies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/673586455b06fe393a3cbbc7f7ff1243.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/673586455b06fe393a3cbbc7f7ff1243.webm?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/673586455b06fe393a3cbbc7f7ff1243.mp4?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b639963bfd670d2de2ce74162412f05c.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" width=520 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b639963bfd670d2de2ce74162412f05c.webm?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/edc9e3528a373e0feab6c6ae60d2bf57.poster.avif?t=1773046905\" width=198 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/edc9e3528a373e0feab6c6ae60d2bf57.webm?t=1773046905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
